  "description": "Fix Typography Issues on Plan Zajec Page\n\nReview and correct typography problems on the /plan-zajec/ page to ensure proper text rendering and readability.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all typography issues (font family, size, weight, line height, spacing)\n- Ensure consistent font styling with the rest of the application\n- Fix any text overflow, wrapping, or alignment problems\n- Verify proper rendering across different screen sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Check for missing or incorrect font loading\n- Ensure appropriate contrast ratios for accessibility (WCAG AA standards)\n- Test with different text lengths and content variations\n- Verify proper localization support if applicable (diacritics, special characters)",
